      You might want to check out http://thepeopledecide.is/<br/>It has only been operating for a few months, so there are a few bugs in it's design. But on the whole, this is probably the approach to accomplishing what you are suggestion. <br/><br/>Good two-way communication between the participant and their elected representatives isn't there yet. In addition, each bill listed should have a blog page assigned to it, with some good deliberative groupware working. But this website is simply miles ahead of anything I have seen covering this area, and is definitely worth the read and even joining up.<br/>ex animo<br/>davidfarrar

                  
