      NationBuilder is an open source platform in active development that the government could use for this.<br/><br/>http://github.com/jgilliam/nationbuilder<br/><br/>It will launch as a web service in a few weeks: http://nationbuilder.com/<br/><br/>It is currently being used to experiment with how the White House might work using this here: http://whitehouse2.org/

                  
